            <title>About</title>
            <link>http://localhost:4002/about/</link>
            <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:4002/about/</guid>
            <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hey-im-robin-&#34;&gt;Hey, I&amp;rsquo;m Robin 👋&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;I build things at the intersection of cloud and AI.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Currently a Senior Solutions Engineer at &lt;strong&gt;Microsoft&lt;/strong&gt;. Previously at &lt;strong&gt;AWS&lt;/strong&gt; serving ISV and SMB clients as Solutions Architect, and before that at &lt;strong&gt;IBM&lt;/strong&gt; as Technical Solutions Architect. I design cloud-native architectures, ship AI-powered products, and help organizations make the most of their cloud investment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I care about clean architecture, developer experience, and making complex technology accessible.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When I&amp;rsquo;m not architecting systems, I&amp;rsquo;m writing about what I learn, contributing to open source, or capturing the world through my camera.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;on-this-site&#34;&gt;On This Site&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;📝 &lt;strong&gt;Tech&lt;/strong&gt; — Architecture patterns, AI/ML deep dives, and lessons from the field. Bilingual.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🛠 &lt;strong&gt;Projects&lt;/strong&gt; — Open source tools I&amp;rsquo;ve built: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/sample-China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin-V2&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;CloudFront SSL Plugin&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/deploy-gguf-model-to-sagemaker&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GGUF on SageMaker&lt;/a&gt;, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;📷 &lt;strong&gt;Photography&lt;/strong&gt; — Street, travel, architecture. More on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/robinsu77/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;connect&#34;&gt;Connect&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/robinsujob&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/in/robin-su/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/robinsu77/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;</description>
        </item><item>
